                },
                {
                    "class": "DepictionSeparatorView"
                },
                {
                    "class": "DepictionMarkdownTextView",
                    "markdown": "**AntiDarkSword** defends jailbroken and TrollFools-capable devices against WebKit RCE exploits and iMessage zero-click attack chains — including **Coruna**, **DarkSword**, and **BLASTPASS** — at the injection layer before any payload reaches the app.",
                    "useSpacing": true,
                    "useMargins": true
                },
                {
                    "class": "DepictionSeparatorView"
                },
                {
                    "class": "DepictionSubheaderView",
                    "title": "Protection Layers",
                    "useBoldText": true,
                    "useBottomMargin": false
                },
                {
                    "class": "DepictionMarkdownTextView",
                    "markdown": "- **WebKit hardening** — hooks WKWebView, WKWebViewConfiguration, WKPreferences, and WKWebpagePreferences to cut renderer-level attack surface\n- **iMessage zero-click blocking** — suppresses IMFileTransfer downloads and risky attachment preview generation (HEIC, HEIF, WebP, PDF)\n- **Remote content rules** — WKContentRuleList compiled per-process; default-on for messaging and mail apps\n- **User Agent spoofing** — overrides `navigator.userAgent` / `userAgentData` via WKUserScript; presets from iOS 15 → macOS, Android, Windows\n- **App extension coverage** — Share, NSE, notification content, and iMessage extensions inherit or override their parent app's rules\n- **Corellium VM decoy** — fabricates a plausible `stat` for `/usr/libexec/corelliumd`, spoofs `kern.osversion`, and neutralises env/path probes\n- **Daemon protection** — hooks `imagent`, `identityservicesd`, `apsd`, and `IMDPersistenceAgent` at Level 3\n- **TrollFools variant** — substrate-free build; injected per-app, no jailbreak required",
                    "useSpacing": true,
                    "useMargins": true
                },
                {
                    "class": "DepictionSeparatorView"
                },
                {
                    "class": "DepictionSubheaderView",
                    "title": "Auto-Protect Levels",
                    "useBoldText": true,
                    "useBottomMargin": false
                },
                {
                    "class": "DepictionMarkdownTextView",
                    "markdown": "| Level | Scope |\n|---|---|\n| **1** | Browsers, mail, messaging, WebKit-heavy apps |\n| **2** | Level 1 + social and media apps |\n| **3** | Level 2 + system daemons (iMessage services) |\n\nCustom per-app and per-extension rules override the active level for any bundle ID.",
                    "useSpacing": true,
                    "useMargins": true
                },
